BETA - TEST VERSION

You are taking on the role of Park Ranger. You have been equipped with AI powered cameras that issue Fixed Penalty Notices, as well as a team of litter-picking robot spiders. You have the task of solving ten stages of increasingly difficult litter situations in your park. To complete each stage you must splat all the bugs and clear all the litter. You can splat litter bugs if you can catch them, as well as this you and your cameras can also splat bugs by shooting tickets at them from a distance. Your advanced technology has limited uses per stage, so you must act quickly so that you don't have to manually pick up all the litter after the bugs have all been splatted out of existence. Also be very careful not to hit innocent bystanders with tickets, the cameras do not hit innocent bystanders as they have facial recognition. Only you can save our beautiful park from becoming a wasteland! Good luck!

